reviews.review_text: Sweet Spot Enjoying this listen of this fine AUD, you can hear Keith's contributions throughout, vocals are not distant, the only flaw is the various cuts, but all in all this master AUD is a keeper! It is great to see AUD surface like this one, hope to see more:-)
A Gem Take this one out when have access to good system. Revel in the WOS
